race.comment: SAVVY BEE (14) doesn't win of turn but has placed around this circuit and is usually thereabouts. Will be rock-hard fit for this and should be right there at the business end. BATTLESPACE (12) saves his best form for this mile journey with a win and a second from just three attempts. Will be cherry-ripe now and is sure to give a great sight. BLONDE ON BLONDE (8) strips fitter second-up from the spell and must be respected out of the Vandyke camp. Top-three contender on best form. PRIDE OF SAVABELLA (4) was a touch plain last time out but go on the solid win over this course and distance two back. Worth another chance. BOLSHEVIC ROAD (7) rounds out the selections in a wide open contest.
